OL,3,CTUI urged to review its safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after death of five-year-old
OL,6,FTravel company Tui has been urged by a
OL,7,Fcoroner to review its safety measures
OL,8,Fafter a five-year-old boy died in a
OL,9,Fswimming pool on a family holiday to
OL,10,FGreece.
OL,12,FTheo Treharne-Jones, from Merthyr
OL,13,FTydfil, died after being found in a
OL,14,Fpool at Atlantica Holiday Village on
OL,15,FKos in 2019.
OL,17,FHe had been on a Tui holiday with his
OL,18,Ffamily.
