OL,6,FBut when the family arrived at the
OL,7,Fcomplex late at night in June 2019,
OL,8,Fthey realised this apartment did not
OL,9,Fhave chains fitted to the door.
OL,11,FTheo's parents, who were "alert to the
OL,12,Fpossibility" he could attempt to leave
OL,13,Fthe room himself, placed prams and
OL,14,Fcases in front of the door to act as a
OL,15,Fbarrier.
OL,17,FMs Treharne said she woke up on the
OL,18,Fmorning to hear shouting from outside.
