OL,6,FTheo had been found in the shallow end
OL,7,Fof the pool. He was pulled out and
OL,8,Fresort staff and other holidaymakers
OL,9,Fcarried out CPR but Theo later died.
OL,11,FThe inquest heard Theo had been able
OL,12,Fto use the door handle to exit the
OL,13,Fapartment himself.
OL,15,FThe five-year-old who loved swimming
OL,16,Fhad been diagnosed with the
OL,17,Fneurodevelopmental disorder Smith-
OL,18,FMagenis syndrome, which affected his
OL,19,Fsleep and left him non-verbal, with no
OL,20,Fsense of danger.
