OL,3,CTUI urged to review its safety
OL,4,Cmeasures after death of five-year-old
OL,6,FThere were no lifeguards on duty at
OL,7,Fthe time as the pools were closed, and
OL,8,Fno physical barriers around the pool
OL,9,Fto prevent unsupervised access by
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FLibby Jones, general manager for
OL,13,Foverseas health and safety at Tui,
OL,14,Fsaid it was considered, following
OL,15,FTheo's death, whether to put chains on
OL,16,Fthe hotel doors, but it was believed
OL,17,Fthis would pose fire safety issues.
