OL,6,FMs Jones added that installing
OL,7,Fbarriers around the swimming pool
OL,8,Fcould result in children climbing on
OL,9,Fthem and thereby create an additional
OL,10,Frisk.
OL,12,FConcluding, Mr Knox said he would
OL,13,Fissue a Prevention of Future Deaths
OL,14,Freport to Tui and Abta, a trade
OL,15,Fassociation for UK travel agents, to
OL,16,Fencourage them to "reconsider the
OL,17,Fspecific circumstances" surrounding
OL,18,FTheo's death.
