OL,6,F"I'm still concerned that families
OL,7,Fwith vulnerable children, or even
OL,8,Fvulnerable adults, are still in a
OL,9,Fposition where somebody may,
OL,10,Fpotentially unsupervised, leave a
OL,11,Fhotel room and travel without any form
OL,12,Fof barrier to any form of hazard," Mr
OL,13,FKnox said.
OL,15,F"In Theo's case, it was a swimming
OL,16,Fpool."
OL,18,FTui have been contacted for comment.
